name: The First REMIX of These | P0035 #pennydrops
description:
An obverse remix of P0034, itself a Dada/Burroughs-inspired cut-up poem, created from a Victorian copy of The Times newspaper.
⁠
With a gentle nod to Victorian Spiritualism and automatic writing, we're acting as a medium; connecting a physical piece of art to The Other Side - in this case, the digital/blockchain side.
⁠
@quietbritacc | 2160 x 2160px mp4
